      <title>疫情引发的股市泡沫破灭引发了 ETF 倒闭潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/pandemic-stock-bubble-burst-day-trading-fizzling-fuels-big-wave-of-etf-closures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着大流行时代日间交易热潮的消退，臭名昭著的 7.7 万亿美元 ETF 行业今年的倒闭数量将达到第二高。]]></description>
